  "libraryVersion": "2025.06",
  "lastValidated": "2026-06-27",
  "pluginNotes": "ProgressIndicator is a SAP instance. Plugin places via SAP_KEYS. Percent + label injected via setProperties (display.value) when supported, otherwise via text node lookup. State variant (None/Success/Warning/Error) drives the SAP-internal color binding \u2014 when state is set correctly, the fill auto-binds to the right semantic token.",
